data.title: Moolah Beach Cast
data.meta_description: Does anyone have the full list of Moolah beach cast members Instagrams ?  Curious what they are up to now.
data.text:
Post by Cruise meerkat Youssy on

Xavier Yepez

Facebook? Not 100% sure.

I'm pretty sure this is his LinkedIn. If so, he went on to graduate from Marquette University in 2009, and works in technology/engineering in the Chicago area.

Chasati Allen

Facebook

Chasati went on to graduate from Bowling Green State University in 2010. She's worked as a flight attendant for American Airlines since 2015, and is based in the Chicago area. Her Twitter and Instagram are @isthatchasati.

Jacob Capito

Facebook

Jacob lives in Indianapolis and is an emergency medicine physician. He is married to the girl in the picture.

Chloe Levenson

I believe this is her LinkedIn. If so, she graduated from Haverford College in 2009 and got a Master's degree in Social Work in 2017. She lives in NYC and works as a learning specialist at a school.

A.J. Johnson

Facebook

He appears to live in Georgia and is either married/in a relationship with a multitude of children. He is an Afghanistan veteran and active in his faith.

Brittany Harris

Facebook

Brittany is married with a young child; she now goes by the name Brittany Eldridge. She went on to graduate from UCF in 2011 and lives in the Miami/Fort Lauderdale area. She is a sales manager at an insurance company. Her Instagram is private but it's @britteldridge2388.

Drew Luna

Facebook

Drew is married with a young child and lives in the Orlando area. He works for the Orlando police department. His Instagram is private but it's @dlunagram.

Nancy Diaz

Facebook

Nancy went on to graduate from University of Florida in 2008. She currently lives in LA and works as a content manager for Hulu. Her Instagram is private but it's @ndiaz22.

Kyle Searles

Facebook

Kyle is married with a child and lives in the Dallas area. He is a realtor. His personal Instagram is @kylesearles and his work Instagram is @realtordallastx.

Shari Lee

Shari is a professional mariner. No social media that I know of. This is a link to an article about her and her career.

Clark Harrison

Facebook

Clark lives in New York and is married with a young child. He works as a songwriter, lifestyle coach, and entrepreneur. His Instagram is @clarkharr.

Summer Borden

Facebook

Summer is married or in a relationship and lives in Texas. She has profile on strong lockdown so I don't know much more. From what I can tell, she has no Instagram.

Post by crystalclearhawaii on

OH MY GOD. I’m just realizing that Moolah Beach is 19 YEARS OLD and I’m finally seeing what the cast looks like now for the very first time and man these kids have definitely grown.😵😵😵😵😵😵😵😵😵😵😵😵😵

Honestly I think Moolah Beach should get its on board here since without it we wouldn't have Endurance and Karma. Also so I can conduct interviews if I am able to with the contestants.

I second this!! We owe everything to Moolah Beach. It deserves more love!

Post by baronvonluna on

I know I’m a little late to the game here but I came across this post after wanting to see if my website was showing on Google. Drew’s Instagram is indeed @dlunagram, and his business page is @drewlunarealtor, he also runs his own site Destination-Charlotte.com. He and his family moved to Charlotte last fall and he’s now a full real estate broker (no longer the po po)! Full disclosure, this post was made partly for fun, because I am he! I absolutely love that you guys still have a love for MB, if anyone wishes to reach out to me on social media, I’m absolutely open to say hello! Look forward to hearing from you guys.

Go Red Team!

Love,

Drew
